videos.headline: Nisby goes up the middle for 47-yard TD
videos.description: Desmond Nisby takes the hand off  47 yards for a Red Raiders' touchdown.

videos.headline: Shimonek spins out of pocket, delivers 37-yard TD pass
videos.description: Nic Shimonek escapes the pass rush and throws the touchdown on the run to Quan Shorts.

videos.headline: Booker snags Jayhawks' first TD
videos.description: Jeremiah Booker leaps along the sideline and  taps his toe in bounds to haul in a 18-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Allen leaps into passing lane for INT
videos.description: Dakota Allen intercepts Peyton Bender to set up the Red Raiders with good field position.

videos.headline: Nisby powers in his second TD
videos.description: Desmond Nisby pounds through defenders for an 8-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Nisby punches in his 3rd TD of the game
videos.description: Desmond Nisby tumbles into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Martin scores from 2-yards out
videos.description: Taylor Martin comes in and scores a touchdown from the wildcat formation.

videos.headline: Parker returns fumble for TD
videos.description: Justus Parker forces Kansas fumble, picks it up and returns it 20 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Parker intercepts Stanley's tipped pass
videos.description: Justus Parker gets his first interception off of a tipped pass.

videos.headline: Shimonek hits wide open Coutee for TD
videos.description: Keke Coutee is wide open and catches a 40-yard touchdown pass from Nic Shimonek

videos.headline: Nisby runs for his 4th TD
videos.description: Desmond Nisby adds to his big day by scoring his fourth rushing touchdown.
